      <h1 class='title'>Ministry of Defence (Annual Report and Accounts)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 30 October 2003 vol 412 c20WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_20ws' title='Col. 20WS &mdash; HC Deb 30 October 2003 vol 412 c20WS' name='column_20ws' href='#column_20ws' rel='bookmark'>20WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04216'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031030_CWS_6'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-geoff-hoon' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031030_CWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Mr Geoff Hoon' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-geoff-hoon" title="Mr Geoff Hoon">The Secretary of State for Defence (Mr. Geoffrey Hoon)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04216">Information about the Ministry of Defence's performance during the last financial year is contained in the Ministry of Defence Annual Report and Accounts for 2002&#x2013;03, which will be laid before the House today as HC 1125.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-04217">Copies will be placed in the Libraries of both Houses and it will also be available on the Ministry of Defence website.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
